      "raw_text": "tScripps News Association.)\n\n\nTELLURIDE, Col, March 20\nPresident Meyer of the Western Fed\nGrafton of Miners is still prisoner\nin Jail here. No effort has been made\nto secure bondsmen. Attorney Murphy\nof Denver arrived last night to defend\nMeyer. He was Immediately waited\non by a number of men and warned\nto leave the district. He appealed to\nGeneral Bell for protection and is now\nescorted by a squad of soldiers.\n\n\nFive deported unionists who at\ntempted to return to Telluride were\narrested by the military at Ophir\nLoop and thrown into the bullpen."
    }
